c: 11
v: 44
t: (Ng'ebitonde bimaze okuzikirira) waalangirirwa nti owange ttaka mira amazzi naawe ggulu lekera awo okutonnyesa enkuba era amazzi gaakalira ensonga neekoma awo eryato neritereera ku lusozi oluyitibwa Juudi era newalangirirwa nti okwesamba okusaasira kwa Katonda kubeere ku bantu abeeyisa obubi